text:
Bhai!!!
kitni to yadein hain yaar sab kaise likh sakta hun yahan. Tu bahut sweet or bakchod aadmi hai bee or tere saath saara time kya hi mja aata tha...TT, Songs, Nightout, Saath me bhand....or bahut kuch. Bhai plan to bahut gaane krne ka tha pr iss vacation me jyaada ho nahi paaya..afsos. 
You will be missed <3<3... Milna to hai hi apne ko phir se jaldi.
Stay happy always and stay same. BC agar badla to guitar bhi mai hi bajaunga or gaaunga bhi mai hi or tu bass stories daalte rehna...hahhahaha...
Teri shaadi me apna waala gaana (Mere Kareeb) gaayenge apan do...yaad rakhna ye baat.
